    "stat_block": {
        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "This small piece of wood is finely carved to depict a foxglove. The spell DC of any spell cast by Activating this item is 17. \n* **Armor** You gain resistance 2 to poison damage.\n* **Weapon** After you cast a plant spell by activating the foxglove token, your Strikes with the weapon it's attached to deal an additional 1d4 poison damage until the end of your next turn.",
